# 👨‍👩‍👧 Basic Family Tree

```text
                 Grandfather ───── Grandmother
                        │
          ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐
       Father                     Uncle
          │
     ┌────┴─────┐
   You       Sister

Uncle
│
├── Cousin
└── Cousin
```

