# 🔍 Dry Run 4

Question

A is the brother of B.

B is the sister of C.

C is the father of D.

Family Tree

```text
        Parents

      /    |    \

     A     B     C

                │

                D
```

Relationship

```text
A

↓

Brother of D's Father

↓

Uncle
```

Answer

```text
Uncle
```

