# ❌ Common Mistakes

🔴 Solving without drawing a family tree.

🔴 Confusing "only son" with "only child."

🔴 Ignoring words like "only."

🔴 Confusing Uncle and Cousin.

🔴 Forgetting that the speaker may refer to themselves.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

